description:
Google IO 17 Extended, Chlef

We'll start off with a 10-minute video highlights reel of the Google I/O Keynote which covers the key product announcements. Following that, we will have 1 hour Developer Keynote then some selected sessions about Android, VR and Progressive Web Apps.

PIZZA AND BEVERAGES ARE INCLUDED :)

name: DevFest Algeria Center 2017
description:
GDG DevFest Algeria Center 2017 is our annual 2 Days of developer conferences that offers speaker sessions across multiple Google Product Areas and Technologies, Codelabs, Talks and more !

to Get Invitations, Please Register Here : https://goo.gl/o9qKqC

We will rock Google Technologies going through developers favorite and trending tools from Google Assistant to VR&AR Products, Bringing Android News to the Front and Mixing it with Firebase, PWA, Google Cloud Platform, not forgetting about Tensorflow and the awesome web frameworks AngularJS and Polymer !
